{"tid":2026134,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【和你計】黃色經濟圈 單計零售就估值過千億？","createTime":"2020-05-20T17:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T12:03:05.000Z","uid":67295,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2c0a237328407fbc3a36707719bb68fa44c60b","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T17:59:21.000Z","msg":"大家好 喺大家睇依篇野之前要戴返個頭盔先<br />\n手足我唔係讀統計出身 之前都無計過依啲野<br />\n純粹見Bloomberg篇文<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">1</span>講咗好多黃色經濟圈對零售業極大既幫助<br />\n再加上沈旭暉佢對黃色經濟圈既估值過千億<br />\n就想自己計返條數出黎俾大家Fact Check<br />\n加上我個港豬老母成鳩日話杯水車薪 我就想證明俾佢睇Every bit helps<br />\n都想繼續鼓勵大家係生活上既每一方面都繼續支持黃色經濟圈<br />\n好啦講多無謂 我地一齊計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每年我地個仆街政府都會出份香港零售業既調查報告<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">2</span><br />\n而咁啱三月份既又出咗喇 我就用咗依個數據黎計<br />\n根據香港政府統計處既零售業銷貨額按月統計調查報告<br />\n原來單計超級市場依樣<br />\n由上年八月到今年三月既八個月銷貨價值就已經達到374億！<br />\n而依個數係唔包服裝、電器等等<br />\n<br />\n當然啦，我地生活唔係只有超級市場。我係依度再加上一啲大家日常生活會用既野：<br />\n電器及其他未分類耐用消費品： 258.51億<br />\n衣物、鞋類及有關製品： 250.76億<br />\n食品、酒類飲品及煙草 (超級市場除外)： 280.87億<br />\n書報、文具及禮品： 38.82億<br />\n眼鏡店： 14.83億<br />\n藥物及化妝品： 205.83億<br />\n<br />\n姐係單計以上八個月係零售業既Categories香港人既銷貨價值就已經達到1424億<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">－</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我當有五成<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">＋</span>消費金額係黃色經濟圈<br />\n姐係單計上年八月到今年三月我地既銷貨價值就已經去到712億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我拉返開一年既金額姐係712＊3／2＝1068億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依個數仲要未計我地最引以為傲既餐飲業！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依一千億我地每一個有幫襯既都有付出<br />\n係，我地失去好多手足 好多方面都要繼續努力 先對得住依家上緊庭既 甚至係裁決完既手足<br />\n不過起碼係最簡單既黃色經濟圈入面我地都可以盡自己最大努力<br />\n將生活每一方面都同運動環環相扣 唔好覺得自己既努力係無濟於事<br />\n屌自己老豆老母 同佢地講我地真係無咗一個都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兄弟爬山，起碼係經濟圈依方面 我地係對得住手足<br />\n屌撚到中聯辦fak fak聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">＊註：攞八月到三月係因為鄰國遊客少啲 個數大約係香港人洗既數<br />\n－註：好多行業我都唔係太熟或者唔識點計所以無加落去，包括（汽車及汽車零件、傢具及固定裝置同百貨公司等等）<br />\n＋註：依度當然無得好準確咁計 我攞五成係基於香港選民有6成係民主派<br />\n而監警會報告都再次證實六成幾係支持成個運動（佢有幾bias大家有目共睹 咁樣我地都六成幾） 反對既只有不到兩成 中立既都係大約兩成<br />\n我當大部份手足都幫襯返黃店 藍絲因為無一個好established既經濟圈 再加上自私既本性 所以點都間唔中幫襯返我地</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">References:<br />\n1Bloomberg : <a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2020-05-20/hong-kong-protesters-helped-local-businesses-survive-coronavirus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2020-05-20%2Fhong-kong-protesters-helped-local-businesses-survive-coronavirus&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=62d8043f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2020-05-20/hong-kong-protesters-helped-local-businesses-survive-coronavirus</a><br />\n2零售業銷貨額按月統計調查報告 : <a href=\"https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B10800032020MM03B0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB10800032020MM03B0100.pdf&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=6208ff55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B10800032020MM03B0100.pdf</a></span>"},{"pid":"d8d6db4a77456593040fa10d7915a38dae322f10","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:00:39.000Z","msg":"有乜野計錯唔好屌得太大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時如果大家有乜野想我下次計都可以同我講聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb756f61fdb75c468fea9a3f710965b0832eb19","tid":2026134,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9363fbcdd24a79f8ce22e5f4505131539a9ee881","tid":2026134,"uid":358760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0403e12b0d26bcadb920a36d4939fd036da9b37e","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9363fbcdd24a79f8ce22e5f4505131539a9ee881","tid":2026134,"uid":358760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依個都係保守估計 想同大家講黃色經濟圈係我地其中一個要堅持既野"},{"pid":"46cbcfbb4398d6a444c7211c468e0ff09c9e0409","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746bfbd985155d4e0b2f7fa0f6d086c111e0c730","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3b79ef7436ff1f5e9f53f02651de85d6b8f1a2","tid":2026134,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"黃圈其實無你想像中咁大，好多手足仲係搵唔到黃店支持，經濟圈救唔到612就知其實真係唔夠大。"},{"pid":"4150419cc64a8a4ed20fd5b93db282a6ba5700b2","tid":2026134,"uid":24572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:28:38.000Z","msg":"其實黃店要支援返抗爭者先係一個完整嘅經濟圈<br />\n希望多啲有錢賺嘅黃店捐返少少收入俾612依啲組織<br />\n當然每個消費者自己都可以養成定時捐錢依個習慣"},{"pid":"a8f7d83e8482e9aeba1b97a325cda32b78368af7","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8e3b79ef7436ff1f5e9f53f02651de85d6b8f1a2","tid":2026134,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"黃圈其實無你想像中咁大，好多手足仲係搵唔到黃店支持，經濟圈救唔到612就知其實真係唔夠大。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:28:56.000Z","msg":"係啊 不過始終都淨係開始咗幾個月<br />\n好多範其實都未做到<br />\n所以每一個有能力既都要盡力擴大黃色經濟圈<br />\n當佢大到一定規模先可以支撐到全部手足"},{"pid":"ea6633ef580aad09ada0a18127772ab7e6166857","tid":2026134,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:35:59.000Z","msg":"國歌法都黎廿三條又等住上，宜家可能連等店舖轉黃嘅時間都唔會有。"},{"pid":"6ed065facc9d58385200c3e8161ab3d9630ac817","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4150419cc64a8a4ed20fd5b93db282a6ba5700b2","tid":2026134,"uid":24572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:28:38.000Z","msg":"其實黃店要支援返抗爭者先係一個完整嘅經濟圈<br />\n希望多啲有錢賺嘅黃店捐返少少收入俾612依啲組織<br />\n當然每個消費者自己都可以養成定時捐錢依個習慣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:36:55.000Z","msg":"的確<br />\n我覺得每個人都應該有定時捐錢依個習慣<br />\n黃店老細講到尾都係份工 賺咗就捐應該同各位手足睇齊<br />\n我覺得可以做得更多既係從supply chain果度開始擴大黃色經濟圈 同埋真係請更多黃手足"},{"pid":"a4c730b1621c9ae4a0b745c12d7e2bba66d316bc","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea6633ef580aad09ada0a18127772ab7e6166857","tid":2026134,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:35:59.000Z","msg":"國歌法都黎廿三條又等住上，宜家可能連等店舖轉黃嘅時間都唔會有。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:42:17.000Z","msg":"無辦法都要照做<br />\n我地行到依家每一個step都係見步行步<br />\n惡法當然要反<br />\n日常生活既佢短時間殺唔晒全部黃店<br />\n襯依家仲有抗爭機會就盡力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff379f2285f7d2dab311955ecbec545ecfcaf2a","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T20:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da53b4e006cf6abc1487035b29aaa9210468450","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T23:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf203792628bdff71fd7994ca9629e6b756fff6","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:18:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6af4bcdb16398716716d3b98188102b583936a92","tid":2026134,"uid":43668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"好多去撚左地產佬到呀屌"},{"pid":"e7f3aa075d66d14373eb7ffb905088c6569e9caf","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6af4bcdb16398716716d3b98188102b583936a92","tid":2026134,"uid":43668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"好多去撚左地產佬到呀屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"我依度淨係計咗零售既幾個方面<br />\n地產無辦法"},{"pid":"4be54f4976de456b2d651949ffe75154563f88ed","tid":2026134,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:22:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ec6df3ebe362319a8fbea2de7b086617f5604582","tid":2026134,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:24:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb3875515f02cc641557e45d0e6ff0cc3b6ec79a","tid":2026134,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0403e12b0d26bcadb920a36d4939fd036da9b37e","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9363fbcdd24a79f8ce22e5f4505131539a9ee881","tid":2026134,"uid":358760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依個都係保守估計 想同大家講黃色經濟圈係我地其中一個要堅持既野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:27:08.000Z","msg":"你咁正經回佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af89bbd39685ffa615bf0ebb1fe9f072bc56c486","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb3875515f02cc641557e45d0e6ff0cc3b6ec79a","tid":2026134,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0403e12b0d26bcadb920a36d4939fd036da9b37e","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9363fbcdd24a79f8ce22e5f4505131539a9ee881","tid":2026134,"uid":358760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依個都係保守估計 想同大家講黃色經濟圈係我地其中一個要堅持既野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:27:08.000Z","msg":"你咁正經回佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:30:31.000Z","msg":"認真咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06452ef1326bf1617eae3d75534e10c99eb0cf18","tid":2026134,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83ed96bebe4bb5a6f2bea30e99029b0a137add5","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff166536c3b05515fa12b4a4172068c19a84d39e","tid":2026134,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"推"}]}